fields.label: Multi column
fields.name: multiColumn
fields.instructions: Check this if you want multi column support within this form.

sub_fields.label: Filetypes
sub_fields.name: filetypes
sub_fields.instructions: Enter the allowed filetypes, for more information click here.

fields.label: Message
fields.name: message
fields.instructions: Here's where you can format your mail message template. This template accepts any HTML, as long as it's compatible with being displayed from e-mail clients. If you want to insert a variable please use the following syntax: {{ field }}.

fields.label: Send copy to respondent
fields.name: sendCopy
fields.instructions: Set this to <u>true</u> if the respondent should also receive a copy of this e-mail.

fields.label: Field: Name
fields.name: nameField
fields.instructions: Add the name of the field used for the respondent's name.

fields.label: Field: E-mail
fields.name: emailField
fields.instructions: Add the name of the field used for the respondent's email.

fields.label: Usage
fields.message: These fields will hold the error message that will be returned to the user's end. When left empty, the fields will return the placeholders.
